{"tid":1242802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！入嚟投票！打贏輿論戰！(etnet整合！)","createTime":"2019-06-19T07:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:49:46.000Z","uid":45788,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b72b4787debd4831646497dc1650071da02aa057","tid":1242802,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"手足！！<br />\n入嚟投票<br />\n唔好輸！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府新聞處昨晚發聲明表示，重申已暫緩修訂條例，行政長官亦因政府工作上不足令社會出現很大的矛盾和紛爭，為此向市民致歉，你接受嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php%3Fid%3D1189&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8df3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=1c73c457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1189</a><br />\n<br />\n你認為警方於6月12日的警民衝突中有否使用過度武力? <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php%3Fid%3D1188&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8df3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=932beb44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1188</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員陳淑莊在2014年佔領中環一案中，被裁定兩項煽感公眾妨礙罪名成立，被判入獄8個月，緩刑兩年。你點睇判刑? <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Fvoting.php%3Fid%3D1187&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8df3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=28a647a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/voting.php?id=1187</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反逃犯條列引起本港及世界各地多人遊行示威, 你認為港府應否擱置草案? <br />\n<a href=\"http://ww